com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface RemoteSubordinate

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject, ReplicationSubordinate
All Known Subinterfaces:
ItemRemoteSubordinate, RequestRemoteSubordinate
public interface RemoteSubordinate
extends ReplicationSubordinate

Represents the definition of a remote subordinate site.

Note: This interface only provides sufficient information to represent remote subordinate sites used by baseline replication. To represent remote subordinate sites used by item replication, you must use the ItemRemoteSubordinate interface.
